            "reviews": "“A dystopian steampunk golf game.” PERRRRRR-DOOIIIIIIIINNGGG! My heart’s back up where it belongs!”<br><a href=\"http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2014/02/06/hands-on-vertiginous-golf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Rock Paper Shotgun</a><br><br>“I think it's safe to say that Vertiginous Golf is one of the most unique mini-golf titles I've ever played, and its steampunk setting is the real capper to such an off-the-wall and rich concept. I'm quite fond of its approach to narrative within a mini-golf game.”<br><a href=\"http://www.destructoid.com/dystopian-steampunk-mini-golf-is-now-a-thing-in-vertiginous-golf-289971.phtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Destructiod</a><br><br>“Its puzzling, challenging, and deeply weird characteristics make for a unique and engaging experience that brings new life to the staidest of sports”<br>7 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/vertiginous-golf-review/1900-6416129/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GameSpot</a><br>",
